<h2 style="font-size: 22px;">Marlboro College</h2>
<strong>Marlboro, VT</strong>

<div class="infolines">
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers credit for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-green">Yes</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers placement into higher-level courses for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-green">Yes</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
</div>


<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Marlboro awards credit for most exams with scores of 4 or 5.  Marlboro College will grant 8 credits for Advanced Placement Examinations with a score of 4 or 5. There is a limit of 16 credits total. These credits will not be applied to the Plan of Concentration.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.marlboro.edu/resources/handbook/college_handbook/#h.iso6q4-ku2534" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

